                "post_type": "page",
                "content_format": "blocks",
                "content": "<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":2} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Summer Cookout Plan</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Join us for a relaxed neighborhood summer cookout in the park. We'll fire up the grill, share homemade sides, and spend the afternoon catching up with neighbors over good food and lawn games. Everyone on the block is welcome, and there's no pressure to bring anything fancy \u2014 just yourself and an appetite.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Confirm headcount and gather RSVPs from neighbors.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Shop for burgers, buns, drinks, and grilling supplies.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Set up tables, chairs, and lawn games the morning of the cookout.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n</ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\n<!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\">View menu</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->"
            }
        }
    ],
